<section class="fullpage slide" id="about">
    {#        <div class="background-overlay"></div> #}
    <div class="container">
        <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row mb-5 fs-4 align-items-end" id="intro">
            <div class="image-wrapper">
                <img src="{{ asset('build/images/2023-06-22.jpg') }}" alt="Alex Seif, freelance web developer"
                     width="600" >
            </div>
            <div class="ps-5 bg-opacity-75 bg-black p-5">
                <h1 class="fw-bold">Freelance Web Developer</h1>
                <p class="text-md-start">
                    Hi, I'm <span class="fw-bold">Alex Seif</span>, a passionate freelance web developer based
                    in Cairo, Egypt. With over
                    <span class="h3">20 years</span> of experience, I've been dedicated to crafting exceptional
                    online experiences for businesses and individuals around
                    the world.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row gap-5 justify-content-star p-5" id="number-boxes">
            <div>
                <span class="fs-1 fw-bold">20 Years</span>
                <p>WOW, 20 years! I'm grateful for all the creativity and impact I've witnessed. Working with amazing
                    clients. Ready for more adventure.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="" >
                <span class="fs-1 fw-bold">+42,000 Hrs</span>
                <p>With a dedication to every project, I've logged over <span class="bold">42,000</span> hours,
                    ensuring each line of code contributes to the success of the final product.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="" >
                <span class="fs-1">+400 Projects</span>
                <p>Worked on over <span class="bold">400</span> projects with 100s of clients, my work has reached
                    over 250M+ Users & devices from business sizes, markets and industries.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr/>
        {% for section in aboutSections %}
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col p-5">
                    <h2>{{ section.title }}</h2>
                    <p class="fs-5">{{ section.description }}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col bg-black bg-opacity-25 p-5 {{ cycle(['', 'order-last order-md-first'], loop.index0) }}">
                    <div class="{{ cycle(['fs-1','fs-1','fs-5', 'fs-4'], loop.index0) }}">
                        {% for region in section.tags %}
                            <span class="badge text-wrap">{{ region }}</span>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr/>
        {% endfor %}
    </div><!-- .x-container -->
</section>
